# CosHub — project context

Project knowledge lives in `.ai/`. **Read the relevant `.ai/` files before non-trivial work** — do not guess commands, conventions, or architecture.

**`.ai/` file index** — listed in `CLAUDE.md` at the repo root (do not duplicate the list here).

Cursor-specific notes:
